quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  10,107,"and ‘If God touches you with harm, none can undo it except Him. And if He intends good for you, none can withhold His bounty. He grants it to whoever He wills of His servants. And He is the All-Forgiving, Most Merciful.’”"
  10,108,"Say, ˹O Prophet,˺ “O humanity! The truth has surely come to you from your Lord. So whoever chooses to be guided, it is only for their own good. And whoever chooses to stray, it is only to their own loss. And I am not a keeper over you.”"
  10,109,"And follow what is revealed to you, and be patient until God passes His judgment. For He is the Best of Judges"
  11,1,"Alif-Lãm-Ra. ˹This is˺ a Book whose verses are well perfected and then fully explained. ˹It is˺ from the One ˹Who is˺ All-Wise, All-Aware"
  11,2,"˹Tell them, O Prophet,˺ “Worship none but God. Surely I am a warner and deliverer of good news to you from Him"
  11,3,"And seek your Lord’s forgiveness and turn to Him in repentance. He will grant you a good provision for an appointed term and graciously reward the doers of good. But if you turn away, then I truly fear for you the torment of a formidable Day"
  11,4,To God is your return. And He is Most Capable of everything.”
  11,5,"Indeed, they enfold ˹what is in˺ their hearts, ˹trying˺ to hide it from Him! But even when they cover themselves with their clothes, He knows what they conceal and what they reveal. Surely He knows best what is ˹hidden˺ in the heart"